            "title": "盤中速報 - GOGOLOOK(6902)大漲7.36%，報87.5元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>GOGOLOOK(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6902:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6902\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6902-TW</a>)23日11:56股價上漲6元，報87.5元，漲幅7.36%，成交331張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>GOGOLOOK(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6902:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6902\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6902-TW</a>)所屬產業為數位雲端，主要業務為AI 信任雲服務。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌21.63%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌0.27%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+20 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+23 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-3 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
